ed="T" n="0877a07"/><persName key="A013699">釋惟實</persName>，姓<name>湯</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012060">富陽</placeName>人<ptr target="#n3230"/>。其為人也，杜多<ptr type="glossary" target="#g566"/>其<lb
ed="T" n="0877a08"/>行，禪觀其心，淡然靜居，長坐不寐。初母氏<lb
ed="T" n="0877a09"/>抑其願心，不容披削<ptr target="#n3231"/>。既而籠開鳥逝，岸穴<lb
ed="T" n="0877a10"/>泉飛，學<persName key="A007249">善財</persName>之遍參，同<persName key="A002188">迦葉</persName>之練行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1696"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name><lb
ed="T" n="0877a11"/>中</date>往<placeName key="PL000000055085"><placeName>明州</placeName><placeName>若<g ref="#Z1286"/>山</placeName></placeName><ptr target="#n3232"/>，夜聞冥告曰：「<placeName key="PL000000055918">達蓬</placeName>聖跡<lb
ed="T" n="0877a12"/>名山，宜矣！」翌日且登<ref type="place" target="#PL000000055918">其山</ref>，巖洞窈窕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g781"/>，石壁削<lb
ed="T" n="0877a13"/>成，秀異之多，實維靈境。有大佛足跡，詢其山<lb
ed="T" n="0877a14"/>叟，則曰「彼<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>年中</date>始現斯瑞」。遂願捿此，<lb
ed="T" n="0877a15"/>有終焉之志<ptr target="#n3233"/>。時屬海寇<persName key="A010998">袁晁</persName>蜂螘屯聚<ptr target="#n3234"/>，分<lb
ed="T" n="0877a16"/>以剽劫，殺戮無辜。至于<placeName key="PL000000055051">香山</placeName>，眾皆奔竄。<persName key="A013699">實</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0877a17"/>據榻瞑目，先以大石掩洞門。賊可三二百<lb
ed="T" n="0877a18"/>數，復<anchor xml:id="beg0877sgsz3"/>舁<anchor xml:id="end0877sgsz3"/>巨石闊二丈餘，鎮其穴口。<persName key="A013699">實</persName>起喑<lb
ed="T" n="0877a19"/>嗚，以掌舉之，群盜羅拜以謝之而去。邑民<lb
ed="T" n="0877a20"/>重之，遂立精舍，弗再歲而成<ptr target="#n3235"/>。<date from-iso="+0773-02-01" key="j20034242003806" to-iso="+0774-02-18"><name>大曆</name>八年</date>也，<lb
ed="T" n="0877a21"/>太守<persName key="A013700">裴儆</persName>奏請署<placeName key="PL000000012184">香山</placeName>題額焉，詔度僧七<lb
ed="T" n="0877a22"/>人隷名矣<ptr target="#n3236"/>。以<date from-iso="+0786-10-31" key="j20084442008532" to-iso="+0787-01-27"><name>貞元</name>二年冬</date><ptr target="#n3237"/>示疾，終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012184">寺</ref>，則<lb
ed="T" n="0877a23"/><anchor xml:id="beg0877001"/>跏<anchor xml:id="end0877001"/>趺而化也。春秋六十二，法臘三十一矣。</p>
